              <font color="black">The NCC wing of the college is a highly disciplined unit. This unit is working under the able guidance of Prof. Narinder Jit Singh and Prof. Sandeep Gupta, caretaker of NCC infantry. There are 50 students enrolled in the NCC (Infantry) each year who take part in many social activities like tree plantation, blood donation, etc
          </p>
